1. change the vertical axis label in Fig. 7 (b), fix the Eq. 13 in
  the revised manuscript; 2. Add new results of pure shear case in Appendix A;
  3. page 3, fix typos, use d$\phi$ in the revised manuscript.; 4. define the
  pure shear strain as ${\gamma}=\ln (Lx'/Ly')$, which makes the relationship
  between the components of the stress tensor and dilatancy for simple and pure
  shear the same;

(v2) minor changes, added one figure and expanded bibliography; (v1)
  colloquium-style review on many-body localization; 29 pages, 11 figures;
  comments are welcome

